{"tid":1907944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】韓國 24 小時增 600 確診　累計直逼五千　29 死","createTime":"2020-03-03T02:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T02:50:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eaae0059e7a29ace88c496e2fb7073db0e618eac","tid":1907944,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:50:09.000Z","msg":"韓聯社報道，南韓中央防疫對策本部今早通報，截至今天（3月3日）凌晨零時，全國累計確診  4,818 例新型冠狀病毒（COVID-19）感染病例，較 2 日凌晨零時增加 600 人。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，其中 519 例新增確診來自大邱市，61 例來自慶尚北道。其餘分別是首爾市 7 例、釜山市 2 例、光州市 2 例、京畿道 2 例、江原道 1 例、忠清北道 1 例、忠清南道 3 例、全羅北道 1 例、濟州道 1 例。<br />\n<br />\n迄今累計死亡 29 例，其中截至今早零時 28 例，較前一天增加 6 例，今晨又有一名 78 歲病人不治身亡。累計治愈並解除隔離 34 例，較前日增加 3 例。<br />\n<br />\n南韓的新增確診病例，近日持續超越中國官方數字，成為全球最多新增確診的國家<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B-24-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%A2%9E-600-%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E7%9B%B4%E9%80%BC%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%83-29-%E6%AD%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B-24-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A2%259E-600-%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%2580%25BC%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%258D%2583-29-%25E6%25AD%25BB%2F&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=3eaad377\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B-24-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A2%259E-600-%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%2580%25BC%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%258D%2583-29-%25E6%25AD%25BB%2F&h=8e98146d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B-24-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%A2%9E-600-%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E7%9B%B4%E9%80%BC%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%83-29-%E6%AD%BB/</a>"}]}